  "prompt": "Which is the Best SEO Company in Delhi for Digital Marketing Services?",
  "response": "Choosing the \"best\" SEO company in Delhi can be subjective and depends on your specific needs, budget, and goals. However, here are some **reputed SEO and digital marketing companies in Delhi** known for their expertise and client satisfaction (as of 2023):\n\n---\n\n### **Top SEO Companies in Delhi for Digital Marketing Services**\n1. **Webspero Solutions**  \n   - Specializes in SEO, PPC, content marketing, and e-commerce solutions.  \n   - Known for data-driven strategies and measurable results.  \n   - Website: [webspero.com](https://www.webspero.com)\n\n2. **Marketers Brain**  \n   - Focuses on SEO, social media marketing, and lead generation.  \n   - Praised for personalized and affordable services.  \n   - Website: [marketersbrain.com](https://www.marketersbrain.com)\n\n3. **TIS India (Tech Indian Solutions)**  \n   - Offers comprehensive digital marketing services, including SEO, PPC, and web design.  \n   - Known for its experienced team and long-term client relationships.  \n   - Website: [tisindia.com](https://www.tisindia.com)\n\n4. **Profit By Search**  \n   - Renowned for SEO, content marketing, and e-commerce solutions.  \n   - Focuses on ROI-driven campaigns.  \n   - Website: [profitbysearch.com](https://www.profitbysearch.com)\n\n5. **Social Media Lords**  \n   - Specializes in SEO, SMM, and brand promotion.  \n   - Known for innovative and creative strategies.  \n   - Website: [socialmedialords.com](https://www.socialmedialords.com)\n\n6. **Delhi School of Digital Marketing (DSDM)**  \n   - Offers both training and digital marketing services, including SEO.  \n   - Known for its ethical practices and transparent pricing.  \n   - Website: [dsdm.in](https://www.dsdm.in)\n\n7. **RepIndia**  \n   - A full-service digital marketing agency with expertise in SEO and branding.  \n   - Known for working with both small businesses and large enterprises.  \n   - Website: [repindia.com](https://www.repindia.com)\n\n8. **DigiChefs**  \n   - Focuses on SEO, content marketing, and website development.  \n   - Known for its creative and customized solutions.  \n   - Website: [digichefs.com](https://www.digichefs.com)\n\n---\n\n### **How to Choose the Best SEO Company for Your Needs**\n- **Check Reviews & Testimonials:** Look for reviews on platforms like Google, Clutch, or GoodFirms.  \n- **Ask for Case Studies:** A reputable company should be able to showcase past successes.  \n- **Transparency:** Ensure they provide clear reports and insights into their strategies.  \n- **Customization:** Choose a company that tailors strategies to your business goals.  \n- **Budget & ROI:** Balance affordability with the potential return on investment.  \n\n---\n\nIf you\u2019re looking for a specific type of service (e.g., local SEO, international SEO, or e-commerce SEO), make sure to discuss your requirements with the company beforehand.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
